Data Manipulation & File Imports

📌 What You Will Learn

DDL vs DML — the full SQL command category map

INSERT — adding single rows, multiple rows, FK insert order

UPDATE — modifying data safely with WHERE

DELETE — removing rows, FK deletion order

ALTER TABLE — add, modify, rename, drop columns

CSV Import — bulk loading data via Workbench and LOAD DATA

